WEBVTT

00:12:29.080 --> 00:12:30.280
listening --

00:12:31.080 --> 00:12:32.280
responds.

00:12:33.760 --> 00:12:37.616
"Frank, this is the first time
I'm hearing you say

00:12:37.640 --> 00:12:39.920
that you feel sorry."

00:12:43.360 --> 00:12:44.560
And Frank --

00:12:45.560 --> 00:12:48.800
Frank says, "Yes.

00:12:50.240 --> 00:12:53.880
I am sorry for what I did to your brother.

00:12:55.640 --> 00:13:00.120
One day when I go to heaven
to be judged by God,